A group for open-source software and games.

This group is for people who want to keep up-to-date on [url=en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Open_source]open source[/url] software 
across the web. Here you will recieve notifications on project updates, news, and we pick our own project of the month.

If you wish to edit or add something to the group, you may do so on our 
[url=https://github.com/ROCKNROLLKID/Open-Source-Community]GitHub page[/url] You may also edit the community logo on our 
GitHub page, as well. To do so, please go to our GitHub page, then on the right side tab bar, click on "Issues". You may 
view, edit, and resubmit the community logo there.

You may view the 
[url=http://steamcommunity.com/groups/opencommunity/discussions/0/523897653295885376]list of open-source software[/url] 
that we support in the discussion thread of this group.

If you have any questions, please read our 
[url=http://steamcommunity.com/groups/opencommunity/discussions/0/537402115081502797]FAQ section[/url] first before asking
a staff member.

If you wish to join the community, you may view our 
[url=http://steamcommunity.com/groups/opencommunity/discussions/0/541906348047960743]job board[/url] at anytime.

Any and all credit to anyone who has helped our community is posted on our 
[url=http://steamcommunity.com/groups/opencommunity/discussions/0/598199244886622774]list of contributors[/url] page.

If any would like to translate for us, please view the 
[url=http://steamcommunity.com/groups/opencommunity/discussions/1/523897653319194735/]we are looking for translations[/url]
page.

If you have any software or game suggestions, feel free to post about it. Only open-source software and games are 
supported here!
